<doc>
  <member name="D3D12_INDEX_BUFFER_VIEW">
    <summary>
      <para>Describes the index buffer to view.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>This structure is passed into <see cref="ID3D12GraphicsCommandList.IASetIndexBuffer" />.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/direct3d-12-structures">Core Structures</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_INDEX_BUFFER_VIEW.BufferLocation">
    <summary>
      <para>The GPU virtual address of the index buffer.
D3D12_GPU_VIRTUAL_ADDRESS is a typedef'd synonym of UINT64.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_INDEX_BUFFER_VIEW.SizeInBytes">
    <summary>
      <para>The size in bytes of the index buffer.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_INDEX_BUFFER_VIEW.Format">
    <summary>
      <para>A <see cref="DXGI_FORMAT" />-typed value for the index-buffer format.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>